# ğŸš€ FlowMind

**A Lightweight Multi-Agent Automation Platform for Enterprise Tasks**

[![Python 3.8+](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.8+-blue.svg)](https://www.python.org/downloads/)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)
[![Zero Dependencies](https://img.shields.io/badge/dependencies-zero-green.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/flowmind/)

FlowMind is a native Python automation framework that makes building workflows **simple** without the complexity of LangChain, Airflow, or enterprise tools.

## âœ¨ Features

- **ğŸ¯ Zero Complexity** - Simple task-based API, no abstractions
- **âš¡ Zero Dependencies** - Core package works offline, no external deps
- **ğŸ”Œ Plugin Architecture** - Extend with custom tasks
- **ğŸ“¦ Built-in Tasks** - 7+ ready-to-use task types
- **ğŸ”„ Smart Context** - Tasks share data seamlessly
- **â° Scheduler** - Cron-like periodic execution
- **ğŸ Pure Python** - No Docker, K8s, or containers needed

## ğŸ¯ Why FlowMind?

| Feature | FlowMind | LangChain | Airflow | n8n |
|---------|----------|-----------|---------|-----|
| **Simplicity** | â­â­â­â­â­ | â­â­ | â­â­ | â­â­â­â­ |
| **Offline** | âœ… | âŒ | âœ… | âŒ |
| **Pure Python** | âœ… | âš ï¸ | âš ï¸ | âŒ |
